works.description: Dear Google, you had helped me in the past with the very same website. It seems they have elected to change up the URL name and thus need to send you another request. If needed please go back to my prior requests as proof that I am a legit. When you do a google image search "spinner ring with gears" you will notice that the Image URL and website show up via regular search. As a result, I would like to request that these two URL be removed from search and image search. Please email or call me if needed.
